  -simple-scan-2.32.0.2.ebuild, -simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild:
  Clean up old revisions.

  25 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> simple-scan-3.6.0.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #458984

  25 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> simple-scan-3.6.0.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #458984

  20 Dec 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild, simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild,
  simple-scan-3.6.0.ebuild:
  >=colord-0.1.24 supports scanners via udev. Add some subslot operators. Drop
  old.

*simple-scan-3.6.0 (16 Dec 2012)

  16 Dec 2012; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +simple-scan-3.6.0.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump for Gnome 3.6. Add longdescription/upstream to metadata.xml.

  11 Dec 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  simple-scan-2.32.0.2.ebuild, simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild,
  simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild:
  Use virtual/udev instead of sys-fs/udev.

  04 Oct 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #427544

  03 Oct 2012; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org>
  simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #427544

*simple-scan-3.4.2 (17 Jul 2012)

  17 Jul 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild, +simple-scan-3.4.2.ebuild:
  Version bump with various bugfixes.

  17 Jul 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -files/simple-scan-2.31.90.2-support-non-pkgconfig-zlib.patch,
  simple-scan-2.32.0.2.ebuild, simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild:
  Drop useless support for ancient zlib to avoid autoreconf. As a side effect,
  fixes bug #423705.

  05 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> simple-scan-2.32.0.2.ebuild,
  simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

  14 Jan 2012; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #393007

  29 Dec 2011; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> simple-scan-3.2.1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 393007

